snippet.title: Amber Heard appears to have her dress on BACKWARDS
snippet.description:
Amber Heard appears to have her dress on BACKWARDS as she shops in West Hollywood... after posing topless in bed.
Amber Heard is so stunningly beautiful she looks good in anything, even a dress put on backwards.

On Thursday the ex-wife of Johnny Depp appeared to have done just that as she wore a long, white cotton dress the wrong way while shopping in West Hollywood.

This comes after The Rum Diary actress posed topless on a bed in a very racy Instagram snap.

Even though Heard seemed to have a wardrobe malfunction during her day out, she still looked stylish.
